title: American horror story  coven -Zoe ends the voodoo zombie attack
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: This signifies that Zoe really is powerful. She literally negated Marie Laveu's voodoo.

Scenes like this really drive my belief that Coven should have just been it's own spinoff show. They had so many interesting plot points set up and they just dropped them by either having certain characters do stupid or rash things for absolutely no reason other than "the script said so" or in the case of this, they just dropped it all together.
I love how despite not being the supreme, Zoe still had some serious power in her arsenal
Zoe had all the powers and even more and just because of a simple mistake she didn't became the supreme.
When I first saw this I thought Zoe was going to be the main character and she would end up being the supreme.
